# Testing (Vitest)

## Layout

Tests live in `test/` mirroring `src/` structure. Run: `npm test`.

## Before commit

```bash
npm test && npm run typecheck && npm run lint
```

## Patterns

- Use `FakeDecisionProvider` for LLM-free unit tests
- HTML fixtures in @test/fixtures/; local server: `node ./test/fixtures/server.mjs` (port 4173)
- Fixture config: @agent-qa.fixture.config.json with `llm.provider: fake`

## Coverage expectations

- Schema changes → parse/validation tests
- New actions/tools → execution + rejection paths
- Recovery/bug classifier → severity and run-stop behavior

## Avoid

Trivial assertions that only restate TypeScript types. Test observable behavior and contracts.
